    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car\u2014she\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and only ever hand-washed on sunny Sunday mornings. It\u2019s rare to find one in such incredible shape; she truly looks and drives like she just rolled off the showroom floor. Aside from a tiny, barely-there mark on the rim that you\u2019d need a magnifying glass to find, she\u2019s perfection on wheels. Come have a look and let\u2019s chat cars over a coffee!",
