      "description": "This is a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 power plant with perfectly synchronized individual throttle bodies and a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The VANOS system has been completely overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with TMS plates to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. Suspension geometry is dialed in via Bilstein B16 PSS10 coilovers, providing surgical turn-in response while maintaining daily streetability. Rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance, showing zero copper wear. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory-fresh matte finish. This is a blue-chip investment for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
